<a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tspan\"><code>&lt;tspan&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>U\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/SVG/Element/use\"><code>&lt;use&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>V-Z\n   <ol>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/view\"><code>&lt;view&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/vkern\"><code>&lt;vkern&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n   </ol></details></li>\n   </ol>\n  </section>\n<p>L'élément <strong><code>&lt;polygon&gt;</code></strong> délimite une forme close composée d'un groupe de plusieurs segments de droites. Le dernier point est relié au premier afin de fermer la forme et de relier les traits entre deux. Pour créer une forme ouverte, voir l'élément <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polyline\"><code>&lt;polyline&gt;</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemple","title":"Exemple","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css hidden notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">html,body,svg</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>100% <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">viewBox</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0 0 200 100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Exemple d'un polygone avec le remplissage par défaut --&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>polygon</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">points</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0,100 50,25 50,75 100,0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Le même polygone sans remplissage et avec un contour --&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>polygon</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">points</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100,100 150,25 150,75 200,0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">fill</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>none<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">stroke</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>black<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Exemple sample\" id=\"frame_exemple\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/fr/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polygon/_sample_.exemple.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attributs","title":"Attributs","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"points\"><code><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/points\">points</a></code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      Cette attribut défini une liste de point (paire de coordonnées absolue x et y ) nécessaire pour dessiner le polygone.\n      <em>Type de valeur</em>: <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Content_type\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">&lt;number&gt; (en-US)</a>+ ; <em>Valeur par défaut</em>: <code>\"\"</code>; <em>Peut être animé</em>: <strong>oui</strong>\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"pathlength\"><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/pathLength\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">pathLength (en-US)</a></code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      Cet attribut spécifie la taille totale pour le chemin dans l'unité de l'utilisateur.\n      <em>Type de valeur</em>: <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Content_type\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">&lt;number&gt; (en-US)</a>; <em>Valeur par défaut</em>: <em>aucune</em>; <em>Peut être animé</em>: <strong>oui</strong>\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attributs_globaux","title":"Attributs Globaux","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"attribut_de_base\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/Core\">Attribut de base</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Principalement: <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/id\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">id (en-US)</a></code> et <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/tabindex\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabindex (en-US)</a></code></p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"attribut_de_style\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/Styling\">At